descriptionHTML:
Begin your day with an exhilarating experience by seeking the blessings of the Almighty. Through this app our aim is to pave the path of the divine for the devotees by bringing the beautiful images of gods on your smart watch and to begin each day with a purpose.

Presenting "Goddess Durga Watch Face" which is a unique and intelligent Smart Watch application that features beautiful watch faces with best in class User Interface for customization.
The carefully crafted design of the app syncs up your mobile and your smart watch seamlessly and provides rich user experience making it simple and easy to use.

The unique features of this Smart Watch app are:
• Watch Face can be set to change every hour
• Analog and Digital Dial available
• High Quality and Beautiful images of Goddess Durga
